#. This project supports a poster showing the fixtures or results of a
#. football (soccer) tournament. In all cases, shorter translations are
#. preferred. Country names will be shrunk to fit, but many other fields will
#. just overflow. In general, the translation approach should match that of a
#. newspaper or sports page. Be brief and colloquial, not vebose or technical.
#. We're aiming for a casual readership.
msgid "### overview - see notes ###"
msgstr ""

